{"tid":1535740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷死敵和理非集會日 比國際睇到我地嘅決心","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:09:38.000Z","uid":234509,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6b948ef854f025f4b2ce80b319edf18295bafed7","tid":1535740,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"8、9月係各大聯賽開季嘅日子<br />\n各隊球迷理應好開心期待<br />\n但最近香港社會發生的事<br />\n警察的惡行<br />\n和政府對市民訴求的置若無睹<br />\n都令各隊球迷冇咗睇波嘅動力<br />\n北倫敦打吡的熱情不再<br />\n兩隊球迷由平時的針鋒相對<br />\n變為站在同一條船<br />\n同聲同氣為香港發聲 <br />\n足球作為全球最著名的運動<br />\n其影響力是巨大的<br />\n許多國家的元首、政府的高官都係球迷<br />\n而係香港<br />\n足球的影響力非同小可<br />\n英超亞洲挑戰盃、世界盃等賽事已經可以睇到香港人對足球的狂熱<br />\n因此如果香港嘅球迷聚集在一起<br />\n死敵球迷們築成人鏈<br />\n手拖手集會<br />\n一定可以向國際表達我地的訴求<br />\n而9月22有個檔期<br />\n希望香港球迷們可以一同出黎<br />\n向政府、國際展示我地對五大訴求的決心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WccOhGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWccOhGz.jpg&h=fb6e97d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw有冇手足整文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1617a86d41d5eba395350af77305245d741f1a17","tid":1535740,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56002d12da3457bc1c74d378f073feba3840ff00","tid":1535740,"uid":263058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1443fa2432b58f3696b107daafd86b4b0e429f0f","tid":1535740,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093bbdab9559411c291a91d1027e06e8c30516ed","tid":1535740,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f57c309afe646309756fe86c04edfb85e66644f","tid":1535740,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid